metadata.name: Aeon
metadata.description:
Aeon the creator of all, in he lies the knowable and unknowable, positive and negative, creation or destruction; thus the creation of the Mystic Knights existence.

Aeon is part of the Galactic Clan.
.
Galactic Clan = Legendary Trait 
.
.
There will only be 2 Galactic Knights in the genesis collection.
